item.title: Invictus Games | Your Guide to Team Ukraine Activities
item.description: Invictus Games is only 2 weeks away in Sydney. There are some fantastic opportunities for you, the community, to not only see Team Ukraine compete, but also meet the team members and hear their stories. **COMMUNITY EVENTS | ** **_ Інформація українською мовою | VIEW INFORMATION IN UKRAINIAN HERE_** TEAM UKRAINE ARRIVAL SYDNEY INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT –_ 7 am THURSDAY 18.10.2018 _ Meeting place will be in forecourt outside the arrival terminal and marked by a Ukrainian flag.
